# PRODUCTS

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:3000/products/seeder

### Create a new product
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Authorization: Basic: <email>:<password>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Product 3",
  "description": "A new product",
  "price": 500,
  "stock": 1,
  "category": "smartphone",
  "imgUrl": "http://example.com/new-url.jpg"
}


### Get all products (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:3000/products?page=1&limit=3

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:3000/products

###

## Get a specific product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/8a033943-9dda-4757-96f1-4c87c5ce5be0

###

## Update a product by ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/8a033943-9dda-4757-96f1-4c87c5ce5be0
Authorization: Basic: <email>:<password>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "price": 600,
  "stock": 2,
  "imgUrl": "updated-url"
}

###

## Delete a product by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/8a033943-9dda-4757-96f1-4c87c5ce5be0
Authorization: Basic: <email>:<password>


